Class GamePlayUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • main_files.GamePlayUI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class GamePlayUI
extends javafx.application.Application
implements java.io.Serializable

    Chain Reaction Game

    The following class implements the total gameplay happening after a new game starts. The class is the total implementation of all the processes in the game.
    Since:
    17 November 2017
